{"tid":2138964,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"不要叫 核酸 係叫 DNA 政府想逃避叫做DNA檢測","createTime":"2020-08-04T03:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T05:02:28.000Z","uid":228955,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b81f3d521584e4313291434e69a18700716e0584","tid":2138964,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:38:53.000Z","msg":"不要叫 核酸 係叫 DNA"},{"pid":"08aa9d27339a8e5b312570da80d6ed9d645239cb","tid":2138964,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:45:09.000Z","msg":"應該係RNA"},{"pid":"ac9d322ec3e13fc7efc0e7eaf130fde7d7048c4f","tid":2138964,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b81f3d521584e4313291434e69a18700716e0584","tid":2138964,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:38:53.000Z","msg":"不要叫 核酸 係叫 DNA"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:45:30.000Z","msg":"屌西都唔做檢測, 吹呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a46160bcd3a59b15a8669c5ed4d68a4f7b11b38","tid":2138964,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:03:36.000Z","msg":"係NA"},{"pid":"12bfa00b7ce1c9aa072f2e617089c4f45dce0145","tid":2138964,"uid":44569,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:13:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>I) 檢測病毒基因-（RT-PCR）技術</strong><br />\n<strong>樣本：</strong>深喉痰液或咽喉擦拭液<br />\n<strong>原理：</strong>測試以「即時逆轉錄&mdash;聚合酶鏈式反應」（RT-PCR）1為基礎，旨在檢測病人的病毒核糖核酸（RNA）。這種測試方法的優點有高靈敏度，即使樣本只含有極微量的病毒RNA，也可以在被檢測出來，是臨床確診的標準。<br />\n<strong>時間：</strong>6小時左右<br />\n<strong>技術：</strong>需於化驗室由技術人員操作<br />\n<strong>準確度：</strong>非常高（但受採檢技術影響而降低）  <br />\n<strong>價錢：</strong>相對較高<br />\n<strong>應用範圍：</strong>由於有高精準度和靈敏度，是臨床確診的標準。盈健醫療全線醫務中心，政府衞生署以及本港私家醫院亦提供此類測試方法。"},{"pid":"67b9432bb2698284e650733c2cee14510b99a3c1","tid":2138964,"uid":263485,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:16:41.000Z","msg":"DNA 咪又係核酸，脱氧核醣核酸。"},{"pid":"c0399441f78b5e6409d26e31cf5049b97897c493","tid":2138964,"uid":145273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:17:01.000Z","msg":"DNA係去氧核糖核酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5499f64306247eb811a3077074e7a43f9ed79ca5","tid":2138964,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a7dc112f36212f4cb855230e0a6d32765e6d07","tid":2138964,"uid":143474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67b9432bb2698284e650733c2cee14510b99a3c1","tid":2138964,"uid":263485,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:16:41.000Z","msg":"DNA 咪又係核酸，脱氧核醣核酸。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:17:48.000Z","msg":"RNA 咪又係核酸，核糖核酸。"},{"pid":"bd7328fe3e8b39bf7857c0d74f5a61c1e43c27df","tid":2138964,"uid":143474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:18:32.000Z","msg":"屌呢個post 好撚多個核字<br />\n越睇越怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aeed6a677c285f57aa03538d70a1c67fb4a0e23","tid":2138964,"uid":62259,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:19:06.000Z","msg":"見到支那用呢隻字就代表隻字係蝗語? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d385340f1be3351b680039305d0a9cb3305678cb","tid":2138964,"uid":44569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9aeed6a677c285f57aa03538d70a1c67fb4a0e23